{{Top|leg}}
'''Hexprak''' was an [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] spirit who controlled the rising and setting of the [[Ibleam|sun]], and was the strongest of all spirits.<ref name="GCG">''[[Galactic Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

As a result, "Hexprak" was also a common Ewok name.<ref name="GCG" />

